    "This scenario therefore isolates schema complexity from vocabulary mismatch.",
    "Despite the availability of the benchmark datasets for the Text-to-SQL task described in Section 2.1, and inspired by them, this chapter first introduces the Mondial benchmark, based on a familiar open-sourced database with a complex schema, and a set of 100 NL questions and their translations to SQL queries.",
    "Then, it analyses the Text-to-SQL strategies discussed in Chapter 4 using this benchmark.",
    "The experiments and benchmark are in a Github repository foot_11.",
    "Mondial stores geographic data, with a total of 47,699 instances."
